This function will go in either the build,package, or package_pkgname section
Its purpose is to give greater user freedom
By letting the user decide which program/package can provide or resolve a dependency

Its basically a template for a "virtual package" with some extra logic

Arguments:
Requirement
 What your package Actually Requires; ie: some form of ssl
2 (an array) of packages that can satisfy the dependency

depends_one_of SSL_IMPLEMENTATION providers=(openssl gnutls)
